# Inner Animal Media — core (always on)

**Repo:** `/Users/samprimeaux/inneranimalmedia` · **Worker entry:** `src/index.js` · **Deploy:** `npm run deploy:full` only (not `npm run deploy` alone) · **MCP host:** separate worker at `mcp.inneranimalmedia.com`

**D1 / schema:** Do **not** load table lists in rules (500+ tables). Before workflows, tools, routing, or handlers — **query D1** (`agentsam_*` registry, `d1_schema`, migrations). Missing config → idempotent `migrations/###_*.sql`, not JS fallbacks.

