## Code hygiene (high signal)

| Topic | Rule |
|-------|------|
| Utils | Import `cn`, dates, helpers from `lib/utils` paths — **no barrel imports** into components that the barrel re-exports |
| React | `useState` before `useMemo`/`useCallback` that depend on it |
| Models | No hardcoded provider/model in hot paths — `agentsam_model_catalog` |
| Terminal | Gate with `agentsam_user_policy.can_run_pty`, not `isSuperAdmin()` |
| User data | SELECTs on user artifacts must bind `user_id` or `workspace_id` from auth |
| Python patches | `.bak` first, `Path.cwd().name == 'inneranimalmedia'`, idempotent, one logical change |
| cms-editor | Separate Python worker — `pywrangler deploy`, not `deploy:full` |

